:Class Stark
‚çù THIS PROJECT IS NOT FOR PUBLIC USE YET
‚çù IT HAS NOT YET BEEN THOROUGHLY REVIEWED
‚çù THIS PROJECT IS IN A BETA PHASE

‚çù Fastify-style HTTP router for Dyalog APL, built on top of Jarvis.
‚çù
‚çù Usage:
‚çù   ‚çù First define your functions, ListUsers, and GetUser, and CreateUser
‚çù   router‚ÜêStark.New ()
‚çù   ‚çù Matrix mode (method path handler options per row):
‚çù   router.Register [
‚çù       'GET'  '/users'       'ListUsers'   ()
‚çù       'GET'  '/users/{id}'  'GetUser'     ()
‚çù       'POST' '/users'       'CreateUser'  opts   ‚çù opts is a namespace with metadata
‚çù   ]
‚çù   ‚çù Namespace vector mode (.method .path .handler, and optionally .spec):
‚çù   router.Register (
‚çù       (method: 'GET'  ‚ãÑ path: '/users'      ‚ãÑ handler: 'ListUsers')
‚çù       (method: 'GET'  ‚ãÑ path: '/users/{id}' ‚ãÑ handler: 'GetUser')
‚çù       (method: 'POST' ‚ãÑ path: '/users'      ‚ãÑ handler: 'CreateUser' ‚ãÑ spec: opts)
‚çù   )
‚çù   router.Start 8080

    :Field Public  Handlers      ‚çù namespace where handler functions live
    :Field Public  ThreadMode‚Üê'' ‚çù DYALOG_JARVIS_THREAD: '' (Jarvis default), 0, 1, 'DEBUG', 'AUTO'
    :Field Public  Info          ‚çù namespace with title, version, description for OpenAPI info
    :Field Public  Debug‚Üê0       ‚çù 0=all errors trapped, 1=stop on error in dispatch, 2=stop before user handler, 4=Jarvis framework debug, 8=Conga event logging, 16=stop before response, 32=Stark framework debug, 64=stop before routing
    :Field Public  OnErrorFn‚Üê''  ‚çù if set, called as err OnErrorFn req after Fail 500 instead of resignalling; err is a ‚éïDMX clone
    :Field Private _routes       ‚çù vector of route descriptor namespaces
    :Field Private _jarvis       ‚çù underlying Jarvis instance

    ‚àá Make0
      :Access Public
      :Implements Constructor
      Info‚Üê(title: 'AStarkAPI' ‚ãÑ version: '1.0.0')
      Handlers‚Üê1(86‚å∂)'‚éïTHIS'
      _routes‚Üê0 4‚ç¥''
      _jarvis‚Üê‚ç¨
