    ‚àá spec‚Üê_BuildOpenAPI;paths;r;pathKey;pathNS;method;op;opts;segs;varMask;param;pNS;ct;code;schemaNS;e;respNS;respKey;jsonCtKey
      :Access Private Instance
      ‚çù _Mangle mangles strings into valid APL names; ‚éïJSON will unmangle them
      spec‚Üê(
        openapi: '3.0.3'
        info: Info
      )
      jsonCtKey‚Üê_Mangle'application/json'

      paths‚Üê()
      :For r :In ‚Üì_routes
          :If '_'=‚äÉ3‚äÉr ‚ãÑ :Continue ‚ãÑ :EndIf   ‚çù skip internal routes

          ‚çù Get or create path object
          pathKey‚Üê_Mangle 2‚äÉr
          :If 0=paths.‚éïNC‚äÇpathKey
              paths ‚éïVSET ‚äÇpathKey ()
          :EndIf
          pathNS‚Üêpaths ‚éïVGET pathKey

          ‚çù Build operation object
          method‚Üê‚éïC 1‚äÉr
          op‚Üê(
            parameters: ‚ç¨
            responses: ()
          )

          ‚çù Map metadata from route options
          opts‚Üê4‚äÉr
          op.operationId‚Üê3‚äÉr

          ‚çù Extract path parameters from {param} segments
          ‚çù If opts.params.{name} exists, its schema overrides the default 'string'
          segs‚Üê'/'(‚âÝ‚äÜ‚ä¢)2‚äÉr
          varMask‚Üê'{'=‚äÉ¬®segs
          :For param :In {1‚Üì¬Ø1‚Üì‚çµ}¬®varMask/segs
              :If 9=‚éïNC'opts' ‚ãÑ :AndIf 9=opts.‚éïNC'params' ‚ãÑ :AndIf 9=opts.params.‚éïNC‚äÇparam
                  pNS‚Üê(name: param ‚ãÑ in: 'path' ‚ãÑ required: (‚äÇ'true') ‚ãÑ schema: (opts.params‚çéparam))
              :Else
                  pNS‚Üê(name: param ‚ãÑ in: 'path' ‚ãÑ required: (‚äÇ'true') ‚ãÑ schema: (type: 'string'))
              :EndIf
              op.parameters,‚Üê‚äÇpNS
          :EndFor
          :If 9=‚éïNC'opts'
              :If 2=opts.‚éïNC'operationId'  ‚ãÑ op.operationId‚Üêopts.operationId  ‚ãÑ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.‚éïNC'summary'      ‚ãÑ op.summary‚Üêopts.summary          ‚ãÑ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.‚éïNC'description'  ‚ãÑ op.description‚Üêopts.description  ‚ãÑ :EndIf
              :If 2‚â§opts.‚éïNC'parameters'   ‚ãÑ op.parameters,‚Üêopts.parameters   ‚ãÑ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.‚éïNC'tags'
                :If 2=‚â°opts.tags
                  op.tags‚Üêopts.tags
                :Else
                  ‚éïSIGNAL ‚äÇ'tags must be a vector of character vectors. Depth 2'
                :EndIf
              :EndIf
              

              ‚çù Request body schema
              :If 9=opts.‚éïNC'body'
                  ct‚Üê() ‚éïVSET ‚äÇjsonCtKey (schema: opts.body)
                  op.requestBody‚Üê(required: (‚äÇ'true') ‚ãÑ content: ct)
              :EndIf

              ‚çù Response: 
              ‚çù Could be a vector of vectors (statusCode schema)
              ‚çù Or
              ‚çù Could be a namespace (but names are expeceted to be pre-mangled)
              :If 2‚â§opts.‚éïNC'response'
                  ‚çù(code schemaNS)‚Üê‚Üì‚çâ‚Üë opts.response
                  :If (9.1=42‚àò‚éïATX)'opts.response'
                    op.responses ‚éïNS opts.response
                  :Else
                    op.responses ‚éïVSET ‚Üì‚çâ‚Üë(_Mangle‚çï¬®‚äÉ¬®,‚äÜopts.response) (2‚äÉ¬®,‚äÜopts.response)
                  :EndIf
                  ‚çùrespNS‚Üê(description: 'Successful response' ‚ãÑ content: ct)
                  ‚çùrespKey‚Üê_Mangle‚çïcode
                  ‚çùop.responses ‚éïVSET ‚äÇrespKey respNS
              :EndIf

              ‚çù Error responses: vector of (statusCode description) pairs
              :If 2‚â§opts.‚éïNC'errors'
                  :For e :In opts.errors
                      respKey‚Üê_Mangle‚çï‚äÉe
                      op.responses ‚éïVSET ‚äÇrespKey (description: 2‚äÉe)
                  :EndFor
              :EndIf
          :EndIf
          :If 0=‚â¢op.parameters ‚ãÑ op.‚éïEX'parameters' ‚ãÑ :EndIf

          ‚çù Default 200 response if none specified
          :If 0=‚â¢op.responses.‚éïNL ¬Ø2 ¬Ø9
              respKey‚Üê_Mangle'200'
              op.responses ‚éïVSET ‚äÇrespKey (description: 'Successful response')
          :EndIf

          pathNS ‚éïVSET ‚äÇmethod op
      :EndFor

      spec.paths‚Üêpaths
    ‚àá


    ‚àá Start port;code;j
      :Access Public Instance
      code‚Üê‚éïNS ''
      code.inst‚Üê‚éïTHIS
      code.Get‚Üê{inst._Dispatch ‚çµ}
      code.Post‚Üê{inst._Dispatch ‚çµ}
      code.Put‚Üê{inst._Dispatch ‚çµ}
      code.Delete‚Üê{inst._Dispatch ‚çµ}
      code.Patch‚Üê{inst._Dispatch ‚çµ}
      :If _jarvis‚â°‚ç¨
          j‚Üê‚éïNEW (‚äÉ‚äÉ‚éïCLASS ‚éïTHIS).##.Jarvis
          _jarvis‚Üêj
      :Else
          j‚Üê_jarvis
      :EndIf
      j.Port‚Üêport
      j.Paradigm‚Üê'REST'
      j.CodeLocation‚Üêcode
      j.RESTFailProcessing‚Üê1
      j.Debug‚Üê+/(1 4 8 16)√ó1=2|‚åäDebug√∑1 4 8 16   ‚çù forward bits 1,4,8,16; bit 2 is replaced by Stark's bit 64/2
      :If ~0‚àä‚ç¥OnErrorFn
          :If 3‚âÝHandlers.‚éïNC‚äÇOnErrorFn
              ‚éïSIGNAL ‚äÇ('EN' 11)('Message' ('STARK: OnErrorFn "',OnErrorFn,'" not found in Handlers'))
          :ElseIf ~‚àß/(‚äÉHandlers.‚éïAT OnErrorFn)‚àä¬®1(2 ¬Ø2)0
              ‚éïSIGNAL ‚äÇ('EN' 11)('Message' ('STARK: OnErrorFn "',OnErrorFn,'" must be a result-returning dyadic function'))
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
      :If ''‚â¢ThreadMode
          j.DYALOG_JARVIS_THREAD‚ÜêThreadMode
      :EndIf
      j.Start
    ‚àá

